CLI utilities and wrappers for FreeBSD's bugzilla instance with emphasis on 
ports.  Provides a consistent API which can have pluggable backends.

Supported Commands:
 bz login
 bz take
 bz inprog
 bz get
 bz patch
 bz close

 bz overto

Soon:
 bz submit

WWW: https://github.com/pgollucci/freebsd-bugzilla-cli
